I want to know everything,
I want to know everything

12
00:01:09,590 --> 00:01:12,130
I can't fool you forever

13
00:01:12,130 --> 00:01:14,760
I can't keep this hidden

14
00:01:14,760 --> 00:01:19,510
I want to shout out my secret, AHHH

15
00:01:21,430 --> 00:01:23,970
Take that! Telepathy

16
