20
00:01:31,900 --> 00:01:33,730
"Birthday Present."

21
00:01:35,740 --> 00:01:37,530
Here. For you.

22
00:01:37,700 --> 00:01:38,700
Huh?

23
00:01:38,700 --> 00:01:40,660
You wanted these, right?

24
00:01:43,870 --> 00:01:47,080
Thanks! But why?

25
00:01:47,080 --> 00:01:49,500
Today's your birthday, remember?

26
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:51,960
Oh, yeah! I guess it is!

27
00:01:55,550 --> 00:01:58,800
I'm older than you now!

28
00:01:58,800 --> 00:02:00,840
Show me some respect!

29
